Morphology and structure analysis of waste glass, the reduced-waste glass (before acid etching process), and the reduced silicon (after acid-treatment process). XRD patterns of (a) WG (inset: The ICP-OES results of WG), (b) R-WG (WG:Mg = 1:0.7 and 1:1), and (c) R-Si. Inset in (c) shows the yield of R-Si. FE-SEM images of (d) WG, (e) R-WG (WG:Mg = 1:0.7), and (f) R-Si. Inset in (f) shows high-magnification FE-SEM images of R-Si.
